{"tid":797829,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【只會咬牙瞪眼】大陸劇演大反派被嫌惹罵戰 周海媚宣佈退出微博","createTime":"2018-08-28T22:36:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-30T19:22:53.000Z","uid":130626,"like":14,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"f02fc3b3eb770ed89eb09be5a37d80d337fbf585","tid":797829,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T22:36:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180828/large/1535466707_2a43.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180828%2Flarge%2F1535466707_2a43.jpg&h=f71afcd2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180828/large/1535466707_3f82.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180828%2Flarge%2F1535466707_3f82.jpg&h=fed6cbe1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180828/large/1535466707_a7e2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180828%2Flarge%2F1535466707_a7e2.jpg&h=0bcfe453&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180828/large/1535467116_c208.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180828%2Flarge%2F1535467116_c208.jpg&h=d084f3b7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180828/large/1535467116_8339.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180828%2Flarge%2F1535467116_8339.jpg&h=91fefeb2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n近年鍾意返大陸拍劇搵銀嘅周海媚（海味），最近喺電視劇《香蜜沉沉燼如霜》裡面餘演天后荼姚，呢個角色除咗法力無邊之外，仲要係一個大反派，雖然睇到大陸網民都咬牙切齒對天后恨之入骨，仲大讚海味演得好。<br />\n當大家大讚海味演得好嘅同時，唔知係咪有人對海味呢個反派角色入戲太深，有班網民竟然走咗去海味嘅微博，用一啲人生攻擊嘅字眼去鬧爆海味，如「看了這個電視以後覺得你真的好醜」、「大暴牙，噁心死了」、「趕快去把你的大齙牙做了去，演技攔就不說了，牙真是太影響大眾眼睛了」，除咗人生攻擊外，亦有人批評海味演技「感覺不管是生氣還是平靜都只會咬牙瞪眼」、「都老演員了還演成這樣，什麼情緒都要大瞪眼。浮誇粗略。看看隔壁佘詩曼演的壞人。」等等，而讚好同彈爆嘅網民更開始出現罵戰。<br />\n睇見一班網民鬧得咁激烈，搞到海味都心灰意冷，今日喺微博出post，表示自己會退出微博：「成長於一個母親和外婆都信佛的平凡家庭，我從小受到的教育是，做人要善良，也不能被他人欺負。網絡時代，理解情緒大於客觀的輿論生態；身為藝人，把自己的一切交付到顯微鏡下被凝視也是職業宿命。但當思考被情緒裡挾變成潮水方向，我選擇激流勇退。一生何求，誰計較讚美與詛咒。陌生人你好，感謝你的愛意和乖張（義解「不順」或「不相合」），微博再見，繼續我的地闊與天長。」<br />\n海味更在post中張貼咗一條2分19秒影片，影片中有海味出道至今嘅相片，而最後係寫住「微博，再見」。"},{"pid":"0e00b8ea23e2620931d331d77a0e86ed467c98d9","tid":797829,"uid":121496,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T22:54:07.000Z","msg":"寫文章都寫到有懶音"},{"pid":"e818118ffe62cd0e45dfd9a924cf0add0c6a7f71","tid":797829,"uid":67302,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T23:03:52.000Z","msg":"對住班畜生都唔知講咩好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48f77a89f40407c0749bf095c254379e32a6e8dc","tid":797829,"uid":101110,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T23:16:33.000Z","msg":"其實要幾憎一個人先會上佢acc留言屌柒佢本人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c21460881124f0c820c685093d9fed83912201d","tid":797829,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T04:22:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"98a99db4e2ab1539614409c483b6ce99ef1b79b1","tid":797829,"uid":54812,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T04:26:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實要幾憎一個人先會上佢acc留言屌柒佢本人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係<br />\n大陸啲人好得閒 郁啲就屌曬鬼咁"},{"pid":"f4443db2752e4d4e5ffc221417a7692bc3f58f99","tid":797829,"uid":6752,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T04:27:51.000Z","msg":"人生攻擊？"},{"pid":"eee637a97221693b7bb6c01f6867fdaed502f279","tid":797829,"uid":54927,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"quote":{"pid":"98a99db4e2ab1539614409c483b6ce99ef1b79b1","tid":797829,"uid":54812,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T04:26:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實要幾憎一個人先會上佢acc留言屌柒佢本人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosa